              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "Detected a template variable used in an anchor tag with the 'href' attribute. This allows a malicious actor to input the 'javascript:' URI and is subject to cross- site scripting (XSS) attacks. If using a relative URL, start with a literal forward slash and concatenate the URL, like this: href='/<%= link %>'. You may also consider setting the Content Security Policy (CSP) header."
              },
              "help": {
                "markdown": "Detected a template variable used in an anchor tag with the 'href' attribute. This allows a malicious actor to input the 'javascript:' URI and is subject to cross- site scripting (XSS) attacks. If using a relative URL, start with a literal forward slash and concatenate the URL, like this: href='/<%= link %>'. You may also consider setting the Content Security Policy (CSP) header.\n\n<b>References:</b>\n - [https://flask.palletsprojects.com/en/1.1.x/security/#cross-site-scripting-xss#:~:text=javascript:%20URI](https://flask.palletsprojects.com/en/1.1.x/security/#cross-site-scripting-xss#:~:text=javascript:%20URI)\n - [https://github.com/pugjs/pug/issues/2952](https://github.com/pugjs/pug/issues/2952)\n",
